Results.ReviewText:
Who needs fancy coffee shops for great tasting coffee!
The only downside is having to choose from such a great range. 
Thank you Nescafe my kettle's always hot and with so many friends popping in for coffee I'll never be lonely :)
Results.Title: Nescafe is my cafe

Results.ReviewText: I made an excellent choice when selecting Nescafe GOLD Black from the massive range in the supermarket.  I make my coffee strong, without milk and I like the aroma to greet me as soon as it is made.  Nescafe GOLD Black is perfect.
Results.Title: Pure black gold

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking Black Gold ever since it was brought out by Nescafe.  I have tried other brands occasionally but they fail to give the taste I really like.  This is my morning reviver and I won't be changing it anytime soon.
Results.Title: FOREVER

Results.ReviewText: I bought Nescafe Gold Black as I like a strong flavoured coffee and I was not disappointed. I love the smell of coffee and this has an intense aroma, coupled with a delicious taste  thought  was drinking freshly ground beans.
Results.Title: Bold Bean

Results.ReviewText:
Bought a large jar recently after 6 weeks abroad drinking Spanish coffee. Wow the differences in flavour and aroma  were impressive.  The taste of gold blend is truly special-smooth and not at all bitter.
Can't be beaten!
Results.Title: Struck Gold!

Results.ReviewText: This coffee is great first thing in the morning. It's rich dark taste just hits the right spot. It makes a great start to the day, which is what required as a "Wild-scape" photographier helping to capture inspiring photo's
Results.Title: A great morning cupper

Results.ReviewText: I love the taste of this coffee, is very unique and suits my taste buds just right. I will recommend it to anyone and everyone looking for a new taste. Got everyone around swapping what they used to drink to this one only
Results.Title: Best coffee yet

Results.ReviewText: I bought this for the first time about a month ago and I just love the invigorating early morning kick that it gives me. Especially, when my motivation levels are a bit low. Great tasting too. What more could I ask for ?
Results.Title: Great Pick me up.

Results.ReviewText: A friend bought me a jar of this coffee as a thank ,you not my usual blend but so pleased I was introduced to this blend. Real fresh coffee in an instant full of taste and flavour! It’s now replaced my boring old blend.
Results.Title: Great Coffee

Results.ReviewText: I tried this recently and was very impressed. It has a strong taste that reminds me of European cafe coffee. It is much better and more satisfying than the bland generic instant coffee. Rich, strong and full of flavour.
Results.Title: Proper coffee from a jar

Results.ReviewText: I bought this producy 2 weeks ago and I was taken aback by its aroma. Great taste, strong aroma and excellent after taste: just what you need to start the day. I strongly reccomend it if you have a busy and active life.
Results.Title: Fantastic aroma

Results.ReviewText: You don't have to go to a specialist coffee shop for the taste of a good coffee,Nescafé Gold Black has the flavour and the aroma you want from a good cup of coffee.Nescafe Gold Black is why I get up early in the morning
Results.Title: heavenly

Results.ReviewText: I found this coffee to be smooth and rich with just enough of a burnt taste to it. The only issue I had was in ensuring I did not accidently select the decaff. The labels/jar colours are all too similar for my liking.
Results.Title: Tastes rich

Results.ReviewText: I bought this coffee a few weeks ago. The packaging was new so it caught my eye. It was so smooth and really rich and had a lovely after taste, much more intense than instant coffee, will definately be buying it again
Results.Title: Ms

Results.ReviewText: I tried this as a alternative to alta rica and it was a good strong coffee with a slightly more bitter note than alta rica which I enjoyed. I would probably keep buying both so that I do not get to accustomed to one.
Results.Title: taste

Results.ReviewText: I like my coffee strong and boy does this fit the bill. Beautiful smell of the beans combined with a great taste makes this an all round winner for me. Don't just take my word for it, try it yourselves and find out.
Results.Title: Beautiful

Results.ReviewText: I first tried this last week and I am very pleased I did. My main drinks are  water and coffee. A  good choice by my friend who I had a coffee with last week. Will get my own supply when I do my food shop next week.
Results.Title: A wonderful rich smooth taste

Results.ReviewText: I decided to have a change and try Nescafe Gold Black instead of my usual jar. Wow, I am so happy I did. It has a much deeper depth of flavour and is perfect to drink throughout the day. A big thumbs up from me!
Results.Title: Nescafe Gold Black... better than ever!

Results.ReviewText: I have been buying GOLD black for many years, and have to say how disappointing the new style jar is, very difficult to hold if you suffer with problems in your hands, that waistline on the last jar was perfect.
Results.Title: Coffee good - new style jar not

Results.ReviewText: Lovely taste that is strong and packs a punch. It is also smooth and leaves a nice taste in your mouth .Have been trying to buy this recently and haven't seen it around. Looks like new labelling is the reason!!
Results.Title: Nice and strong

Results.ReviewText: This coffee is great for people like me who love strong coffee. It is great quality and has an amazing taste. I usually put 1 heaped teaspoon in a regular sized mug and just add hot water and it tastes great!
Results.Title: Great Coffee

Results.ReviewText: I was looking for a coffee that would revive my tastebuds Nescafe Gold Black gave me the intense taste I was looking for. My friends have been impressed so much that they are now converted to the dark side
Results.Title: Revive my Tastebuds

Results.ReviewText:
I got this as it was on offer and I can say I would now buy this at full RRP. The flavour is rich and robust and lasting on the pallette. Highly recommended. 
Suggestion: add some nutmeg for Christmas =)
Results.Title: Great robust flavour

Results.ReviewText: I usually buy Gold Blend ,but the Black caught my eye, and piqued my interest...  I'm happy I acted on impulse and purchased a jar.. It produces a flavoursome cup/mug(whichever is your vessel)consistently
Results.Title: mighty flavorsome!!

Results.ReviewText: I gave this a try as I was getting bored with my usual brand and found I was having to make it ever stronger to get a decent hit. Not so with this! A very welcome surprise in a world of bland instants!
Results.Title: Best black!!

Results.ReviewText: Just got to have a coffee 1st thing in the morning to fully wake up and this delivers, lovely strong taste and an aroma thats enhances the pleasure, what more do you need? (apart from maybe a 2nd cup).
Results.Title: Priority On Arrival

Results.ReviewText:
I bought this recently and fell in love. A rich, intense, velvety coffee.
A winner from Nescafe, best value, best quality.
We like ours strong and black - nothing else beats it on the market today.
Results.Title: Gold intense coffee.

Results.ReviewText: This stuff just works, perfect for the coffee afficionado (sure that spelling is poor!) when you don’t have time to brew the real stuff. Used it many times in many different places. Recommend highly!
Results.Title: Perfect instant coffee

Results.ReviewText: I brought this 2 weeks ago, and I love it.  The flavour is as expected from Nescafe, rich and strong.  It's an exquisite cup of coffee any time of the day and it's perfect with a nice slice of cake.
Results.Title: Great Flavour

Results.ReviewText: Finding a suitable black coffee that is rich smooth and enjoyed without any after taste or bitterness is not easy. Nescafe Gold Black is now a permanent feature for my pleasure and that of guests
Results.Title: Outstanding richness of a focused black coffee

cb4d59cf-c48d-47ef-a943-50b2ae5d01ee.Description: A rich and full-bodied, premium coffee with strong toasted notes.
cb4d59cf-c48d-47ef-a943-50b2ae5d01ee.Name: NESCAFÉ GOLD Black

Results.Description: A well-rounded, smooth coffee with a rich aroma.
Results.Name: NESCAFÉ GOLD BLEND Instant Coffee
